{"tid":1196190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 站出黎！","createTime":"2019-06-09T18:15:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T18:57:28.000Z","uid":190319,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f7704a2963e0024dd6184a732b548b334bd42c0e","tid":1196190,"uid":190319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T18:15:47.000Z","msg":"一個人力量係微不足道；<br />\n但一群人力量就係力大無窮。<br />\n<br />\n唔好再比藉口自己，放棄成個香港，係時候企出黎，維護自己既家，唔好再比班無良政府繼續改變我地既思想，影響我地既下一代。<br />\n<br />\n只要香港人齊心協力，相信能夠利用國際力量，去改變、去維護自己既家。<br />\n<br />\n6月12號，大家再次企出黎，打壓無良政府，抗惡法。<br />\n<br />\n最緊要個句，大家記住安全至上。"},{"pid":"67c03d0179f06c0f414b53a6f5862fe38235316e","tid":1196190,"uid":190319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T18:19:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"78697493cc6a830610c4dca60cbd6b0a93049fb2","tid":1196190,"uid":190319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T18:20:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e09ac20db2b02dbd6ecf0d5890e9f489aa634e2b","tid":1196190,"uid":190319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T18:20:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52eb1a9cdd763f6e44d9ba5f230c391188657925","tid":1196190,"uid":190319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T18:20:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5191bae6ea5d4687a20e562f73f39c589cf45534","tid":1196190,"uid":190319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T18:20:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cfc97d83d1cb2a252ac483111d45feaefe5a76e3","tid":1196190,"uid":190319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T18:21:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7937074c0e484eb3f1bfeed9920eb373332fefd","tid":1196190,"uid":190319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T18:22:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8dc4c231cf60de650f553cd76f65509e065d157","tid":1196190,"uid":190319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T18:23:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba35852982603b270c7c291524c82a2d32f918a6"